</figure>
</div>
<ol start="3" type="1">
<li>Add custom preferences to RStudio</li>
</ol>
<p>Create a new file called <code>rstudio-prefs.json</code> in the Terminal by typing the following command and pressing <code>Enter</code>:</p>
